<LEADPARA>  HARLEY-DAVIDSON bibs for the babies. Harley ties for the decidedly
unfashionable. High-price rings and leather jackets and knives -- all
emblazoned with the Harley insignia.;    There's more in this store. The
aisles of accessories also contain mugs and piggy banks and lingerie and
