@  Harley-Davidson Price Run-Up Wasn't Fueled
@  By the 'Smart-Money' Crowd, Analysts Say
@  ----
@  By Scott McMurray
@  Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal </HL>
<DD> 10/04/89 </DD>
<SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J) </SO>
<CO> HDI </CO>
<IN> HEARD ON THE STREET (HRD)
